6.00	Melissa_Holbrook_Pierson	Melissa Holbrook Pierson	Melissa Holbrook Pierson, born ) December 14, 1957 in Akron, Ohio, is a writer and essayist of non-fiction. She is a life-long motorcycle enthusiast and this is reflected in many of her books. Her works are often explorations of personal experience, extended into general social commentary and history.	
